# Golden Dataset Design Rationale (이 파일의 설계 의도)
#
# WHY this is a "Golden Dataset":
#   A golden dataset contains questions with KNOWN correct answers, manually verified
#   against the source documents. It acts as a ground truth to objectively measure
#   how well our RAG system performs. Without it, we'd have no way to know if
#   the system's answers are correct.
#
# HOW questions were designed:
#   1. We read both PDFs (2025, 2026) and identified specific facts from tables and text
#   2. Each question has ONE unambiguous expected_answer that can be verified
#   3. Questions are tagged with source_year so we can measure "year confusion"
#      (did the system retrieve from the correct year?)
#
# DIFFICULTY levels:
#   - easy:       Single fact lookup from a table (e.g., "1종 외래 의원 = 1,000원")
#   - medium:     Requires combining 2+ conditions or finding info in body text
#   - hard:       Complex conditions or information buried in less obvious sections
#   - cross-year: Requires retrieving from BOTH 2025 and 2026 to compare differences
#                 This is the hardest category because the system must pull correct
#                 info from each year without mixing them up
#
# WHY include cross-year questions?
#   The two PDFs are ~90% identical in structure and wording. The system WILL confuse
#   years. Cross-year questions explicitly test this weakness. Key differences found:
#     - 장기지속형 주사제 본인부담률: 5% (2025) → 2% (2026)
#     - 노숙인진료시설 유효기간: 1년 (2025) → 3년 (2026)
#     - 외래 365회 초과 본인부담률 30%: only in 2026
#     - 본인부담금 환급 산정기간: 30일 (2025) → 월단위 (2026)
#     - 조산아 지원 기간: 5년 (2025) → 5년 4개월 (2026)
#     - 응급의료관리료 기준: 응급증상 아닌 경우 (2025) → KTAS 4·5 (2026)
#
